Frontend (React):
React:

Latest Version: 18.x
Create React App: npx create-react-app my-app
React Router:

For routing: npm install react-router-dom
State Management:

Redux Toolkit: npm install @reduxjs/toolkit react-redux
UI Framework:

Material-UI: npm install @mui/material @emotion/react @emotion/styled
or Bootstrap: npm install react-bootstrap bootstrap
Form Handling:

Formik: npm install formik
Yup for validation: npm install yup
HTTP Client:

Axios: npm install axios
Authentication:

JSON Web Tokens (JWT): npm install jwt-decode
Others:

React Icons: npm install react-icons
React Helmet for managing document head: npm install react-helmet
React Toastify for notifications: npm install react-toastify
React Stripe for payment processing: npm install @stripe/react-stripe-js @stripe/stripe-js
Backend (Node.js and Express):
Node.js:

Latest Version: 16.x or 18.x
Express:

Latest Version: 4.x
Installation: npm install express
Database:

MongoDB
Mongoose for object data modeling: npm install mongoose
Authentication:

JWT: npm install jsonwebtoken
Bcrypt for password hashing: npm install bcryptjs
File Uploads:

Multer: npm install multer
Cloudinary for image storage: npm install cloudinary
Environment Variables:

Dotenv: npm install dotenv
Payment Integration:

Stripe: npm install stripe
Others:

Nodemon for development: npm install nodemon
Body Parser: npm install body-parser
Cors for handling cross-origin requests: npm install cors
Express Async Handler for async error handling: npm install express-async-handler
Morgan for logging: npm install morgan